\c 1
\s Kurwara nokufa kwaAhazia mambo waIsraeri
\p
\v 1 Zvino vaMoabhu vakamukira Israeri shure kwekufa kwaAhabhi.
\v 2 Zvino Ahazia wakawa nepakarukwa pawindo rekamuri yake yekumusoro, yaiva paSamaria, ndokurwara. Zvino wakatuma nhume ndokuti kwavari: Endai mubvunze Bhaari-Zebhubhi, mwari weEkironi, kana ndichapora pakurwara uku.
\v 3 Asi mutumwa waJehovha wakati kuna Eria muTishibhi: Simuka ukwire kunosangana nenhume dzamambo weSamaria, ugoti kwavari: Imhaka yekuti hakuna Mwari here kwaIsraeri kuti muende munobvunza Bhaari-Zebhubhi mwari weEkironi?
\v 4 Naizvozvo zvino, ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha: Pamubhedha pawakakwira pauri haungaburukipo, nokuti uchafa zvekufa. Eria ndokuenda.
\p
\v 5 Zvino nhume dzakadzokera kwaari, iye ndokuti kwavari: Madzokera chii?
\v 6 Ivo ndokuti kwaari: Kwakwira umwe murume kusangana nesu ndokuti kwatiri: Endai mudzokere kuna mambo wakakutumai, mugoti kwaari: Imhaka yekuti hakuna Mwari kwaIsraeri here, kuti utume kunobvunza Bhaari-Zebhubhi mwari weEkironi? Naizvozvo mubhedha wawakakwira pauri haungaburuki pauri, nokuti uchafa zvirokwazvo.
\v 7 Iye ndokuti kwavari: Murume wakaita sei wakauya kusangana nemwi nekukuudzai mashoko awa?
\v 8 Zvino vakati kwaari: Wanga ari murume ane mvere kasunga nguvo yedehwe pachiuno chake. Iye ndokuti: NdiEria muTishibhi.
\p
\v 9 Zvino wakatuma kwaari mutariri wevarume makumi mashanu pamwe nevane makumi mashanu vake. Zvino wakakwira kwaari, zvino tarira, agere panhongonya yegomo. Iye ndokuti kwaari: Munhu waMwari, zvanzi namambo: Burukai.
\v 10 Zvino Eria wakapindura, ndokuti kumukuru wevane makumi mashanu: Kana ndiri munhu waMwari zvino moto ngauburuke kubva kudenga, ukupedze pamwe nevane makumi mashanu vako. Zvino moto wakaburuka kudenga ndokumupedza pamwe nevane makumi mashanu vake.
\p
\v 11 Akatumazve kwaari umwe mukuru wavana makumi mashanu. Iye akapindura, akati kwaari: Nhai munhu waMwari, zvanzi namambo: Kurumidzai muburuke.
\v 12 Eria akapindura, akati kwavari: Kana ndiri munhu waMwari, moto ngauburuke kudenga, ukuparadze iwe navanhu vako vana makumi mashanu. Ipapo moto waMwari ukaburuka kudenga, ukamuparadza iye navanhu vake vana makumi mashanu.
\p
\v 13 Akatumazve umwe mukuru wavana makumi mashanu; wechitatu, anavanhu vake vana makumi mashanu. Zvino iye mukuru wavana makumi mashanu, wechitatu, akakwira, akafugama namabvi ake pamberi paEria, akakumbira, akati kwaari: Haiwa, munhu waMwari, upenyu hwangu nohwavaranda venyu ava vana makumi mashanu, ngachive chinhu chinokosha pamberi penyu.
\v 14 Tarirai, moto wakaburuka kudenga, ukapisa vakuru vaviri vavana makumi mashanu vokutanga navanhu vavo vana makumi mashanu; naizvozvo upenyu hwangu zvino ngachive chinhu chinokosha pamberi penyu.
\v 15 Ipapo mutumwa waJehovha akati kuna Eria: Buruka naye, usamutya hako. Akasimuka, akaenda naye kuna mambo.
\v 16 Akati kwaari: Zvanzi naJehovha: Zvawakatuma nhume kundobvunza Bhaarizebhubhi, mwari weEkironi, asi hapana Mwari here pakati paIsraeri, waungabvunza shoko rake? Naizvozvo haungaburukizve pamubhedha wawakwira, asi zvirokwazvo uchafa.
\p
\v 17 Naizvozvo akafa seshoko raJehovha rakange rarehwa naEria. Jehoramu akamutevera paushe, akatanga kubata ushe pagore rechipiri reJehoramu mwanakomana waJehoshafati mambo waJudha; nokuti iye wakange asina mwana.
\p
\v 18 Mamwe mabasa aAhazia aakabata, haana kunyorwa here mubhuku yaMakoronike amadzimambo aIsraeri?
